  07 Jun 2015; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> pkgconfig-0.28-r2.ebuild,
  pkgconfig-0.28-r3.ebuild, pkgconfig-9999.ebuild:
  Mark arm64/m68k/s390/sh stable.

  31 May 2015; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  pkgconfig-0.28-r3.ebuild, pkgconfig-9999.ebuild,
  files/pkgconfig-0.28-lfs.patch:
  We cannot use autotools.eclass in pkgconfig, it creates a circular dependency
  (bug #550856, thanks to Fabian Groffen, Mike Gilbert).

  27 May 2015; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  -pkgconfig-0.28-r1.ebuild:
  Clean up old.

  27 May 2015; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> pkgconfig-0.28-r2.ebuild:
  arm stable wrt bug #545848

  27 May 2015; Alexandre Rostovtsev <tetromino@gentoo.org>
  pkgconfig-0.28-r3.ebuild, pkgconfig-9999.ebuild:
  WANT_AUTOMAKE=1.12 is needed for tests if doing eautoreconf.

